puppet

Released 20100709 - Garrett Honeycutt - GPLv2

class puppet         - sets up puppet client - used on all hosts

class puppet::server - sets up puppetmasters
    Monitors a config file that maps your POP to a directory (trunk/tag/branch) in your SVN repo
    which makes it really easy to update your puppet code

class puppet::repo   - sets up a puppet code repository using SVN

class puppet::ca     - sets up puppet CA's which will generate certs for all your clients
    this can be done with the following snippet in your kickstart file (or whatever provisioning
    software you use)

    # setup puppet cert
    curl -k https://puppetca | tar xC /
